00:00:59.410 --> 00:01:04.690 align:middle line:84%
And how I got where I am is some
sort of a mystery to myself.

00:01:04.690 --> 00:01:09.220 align:middle line:84%
Because before 1976,
I was a socialite,

00:01:09.220 --> 00:01:12.520 align:middle line:84%
living in a big, four story
Georgian mansion, married

00:01:12.520 --> 00:01:14.620 align:middle line:90%
to a US circuit court judge.

00:01:14.620 --> 00:01:18.700 align:middle line:84%
And actually, a
