00:01:18.700 --> 00:01:21.450 align:middle line:90%
I have to laugh about that now.

00:01:21.450 --> 00:01:25.585 align:middle line:84%
I wore a French twist,
Neiman-Marcus clothes.

00:01:25.585 --> 00:01:30.790 align:middle line:84%
I drove a Continental Mark III
at the time and a Mercedes.

00:01:30.790 --> 00:01:36.950 align:middle line:84%
And all of my life was taken up
with doing some volunteer work,

00:01:36.950 --> 00:01:39.550 align:middle line:84%
but mostly giving dinner
parties and showing off

00:01:39.550 --> 00:01:42.920 align:middle line:84%
my beautiful four
story Georgian home.

00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:45.610 align:middle line:84%
And when I would
walk in a room, I

00:01:45.610 --> 00:01:49.270 align:middle line:84%
would just stand there,
plastic as I can be.

00:01:49.270 --> 00:01:52.690 align:middle line:84%
It would be, like, I can hardly
even relate to that me now,

00:01:52.690 --> 00:01:56.180 align:middle line:90%
when I think about how I was.

00:01:56.180 --> 00:01:58.750 align:middle line:84%
And one day, over
a Chinese lunch,

00:01:58.750 --> 00:02:01.370 align:middle line:84%
I realized that my
marriage was dead

00:02:01.370 --> 00:02:04.330 align:middle line:84%
and that I had to leave the
only life I'd ever been familiar

00:02:04.330 --> 00:02:05.560 align:middle line:90%
with.

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:07.720 align:middle line:84%
And I remember walking
out of that restaurant

00:02:07.720 --> 00:02:09.580 align:middle line:90%
that day so devastated.

00:02:09.580 --> 00:02:12.860 align:middle line:84%
I really thought that I
was going to kill myself.

00:02:12.860 --> 00:02:15.790 align:middle line:90%
And I stumbled around.

00:02:15.790 --> 00:02:18.070 align:middle line:84%
Went to my best friend's
house and sat in her driveway

00:02:18.070 --> 00:02:19.069 align:middle line:90%
for several hours.

00:02:19.069 --> 00:02:20.110 align:middle line:90%
And she wasn't even home.

00:02:20.110 --> 00:02:21.760 align:middle line:90%
She was on vacation.

00:02:21.760 --> 00:02:24.760 align:middle line:84%
And finally, I drove
home, got in my bed,

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:26.890 align:middle line:84%
pulled the covers over
my head, and begged God

00:02:26.890 --> 00:02:29.590 align:middle line:90%
to just take me out of my body.

00:02:29.590 --> 00:02:33.160 align:middle line:84%
And of course, God
didn't exactly do that.

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:35.770 align:middle line:84%
What actually happened
is a voice boomed

00:02:35.770 --> 00:02:40.120 align:middle line:84%
in my head, a very loud,
masculine voice that said,

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:44.230 align:middle line:84%
go in your study and read
"Discipleship of The New Age,"

00:02:44.230 --> 00:02:49.150 align:middle line:90%
Volume Two, page 146.

00:02:49.150 --> 00:02:51.820 align:middle line:84%
I remember I sat straight
up in bed and thought,

00:02:51.820 --> 00:02:53.230 align:middle line:90%
now I'm really crazy.

00:02:53.230 --> 00:02:55.210 align:middle line:84%
I'm having an auditory
hallucination.

00:02:55.210 --> 00:02:58.130 align:middle line:90%


00:02:58.130 --> 00:03:00.590 align:middle line:84%
Well, it turned out that
I did go in my study,

00:03:00.590 --> 00:03:02.090 align:middle line:90%
and I opened the book.

00:03:02.090 --> 00:03:04.640 align:middle line:84%
And when I opened
it to page 146,

00:03:04.640 --> 00:03:07.130 align:middle line:84%
it said you are one of
the ones who will write

00:03:07.130 --> 00:03:09.350 align:middle line:90%
a book for the new psychology.

00:03:09.350 --> 00:03:12.230 align:middle line:84%
And it gave a little description
about what this new psychology

00:03:12.230 --> 00:03:14.750 align:middle line:84%
would be, that it would
have a much stronger

00:03:14.750 --> 00:03:17.600 align:middle line:84%
evolutionary purpose than
any of the psychologies that

00:03:17.600 --> 00:03:19.050 align:middle line:90%
had come before it.

00:03:19.050 --> 00:03:20.870 align:middle line:84%
And that I would be
guided in this work

00:03:20.870 --> 00:03:25.850 align:middle line:84%
and would write this book in
the crucible of my daily life.

00:03:25.850 --> 00:03:27.380 align:middle line:84%
And I remember
thinking at the time,

00:03:27.380 --> 00:03:29.546 align:middle line:84%
I was supposed to write a
book on the new psychology

00:03:29.546 --> 00:03:31.850 align:middle line:90%
and I'm not even a psychologist?

00:03:31.850 --> 00:03:35.400 align:middle line:84%
And yet I knew, somehow,
that message was for me.

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:36.950 align:middle line:84%
And I think the
main thing about it

00:03:36.950 --> 00:03:41.720 align:middle line:84%
that grabbed me so hard was that
it gave me a reason to live.

00:03:41.720 --> 00:03:43.950 align:middle line:90%
It gave me a sense of purpose.

00:03:43.950 --> 00:03:47.060 align:middle line:84%
And it reminded me of
the self that I really am

00:03:47.060 --> 00:03:48.710 align:middle line:84%
and who I really
came here to be.

00:03:48.710 --> 00:03:53.490 align:middle line:90%


00:03:53.490 --> 00:03:56.310 align:middle line:84%
And when I think back on why
it was that message meant

00:03:56.310 --> 00:04:00.030 align:middle line:84%
so much to me, it's because
my old life had died

00:04:00.030 --> 00:04:03.150 align:middle line:84%
and I could no longer be
the socialite Jacqueline

00:04:03.150 --> 00:04:06.840 align:middle line:90%
that I had been in Texas.

00:04:06.840 --> 00:04:11.880 align:middle line:84%
My life was so transformed after
that time and after that death.

00:04:11.880 --> 00:04:15.540 align:middle line:84%
When I realized I was going to
have to go through a divorce

00:04:15.540 --> 00:04:18.510 align:middle line:84%
and end the life
I was so used to,

00:04:18.510 --> 00:04:21.579 align:middle line:84%
which was very frightening
to me at the time,

00:04:21.579 --> 00:04:24.000 align:middle line:84%
I remember when I plopped
down on the bed that day,

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:28.020 align:middle line:84%
begging God to take
me out of my body.

00:04:28.020 --> 00:04:30.654 align:middle line:84%
I didn't realize it then, but
in looking back on it now,

00:04:30.654 --> 00:04:32.070 align:middle line:84%
I realized what
had happened to me

00:04:32.070 --> 00:04:36.470 align:middle line:84%
is I was in a complete
ego death, which

00:04:36.470 --> 00:04:37.640 align:middle line:90%
can lead to suicide.

00:04:37.640 --> 00:04:42.680 align:middle line:84%
It can lead to such a
discombobulation of the self

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:45.400 align:middle line:84%
that you can wind up
in a psychotic episode.

00:04:45.400 --> 00:04:47.390 align:middle line:84%
And fortunately for me,
mine did not turn out

00:04:47.390 --> 00:04:48.650 align:middle line:90%
to be a psychotic episode.

00:04:48.650 --> 00:04:51.200 align:middle line:84%
It turned out to be
a spiritual crisis

00:04:51.200 --> 00:04:55.280 align:middle line:84%
and introduced me very
experientially to my own soul.

00:04:55.280 --> 00:04:59.720 align:middle line:90%


00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:01.980 align:middle line:84%
When I read the
message in the book,

00:05:01.980 --> 00:05:04.460 align:middle line:90%
I knew the message was for me.

00:05:04.460 --> 00:05:07.320 align:middle line:90%
And it gave me a reason to live.

00:05:07.320 --> 00:05:09.620 align:middle line:84%
It was like a
reminder of some me

00:05:09.620 --> 00:05:11.780 align:middle line:84%
that I've always been that
I had been out of touch

00:05:11.780 --> 00:05:17.540 align:middle line:84%
with, as though I went back
into some sort of cosmic reality

00:05:17.540 --> 00:05:20.780 align:middle line:84%
and remembered why I had come
to this world, what I was really

00:05:20.780 --> 00:05:22.730 align:middle line:90%
here to do and be.

00:05:22.730 --> 00:05:26.570 align:middle line:84%
And even though I didn't have
a support group or anyone

00:05:26.570 --> 00:05:29.540 align:middle line:84%
around me at the time to
help me with this, what I did

00:05:29.540 --> 00:05:31.460 align:middle line:84%
is I began gathering
notes and listening

00:05:31.460 --> 00:05:35.240 align:middle line:84%
to the guidance that was coming
through about writing the book.

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:38.360 align:middle line:84%
And I was so
inspired that that's

00:05:38.360 --> 00:05:42.440 align:middle line:84%
what kept me going until my new
life began to build around me

00:05:42.440 --> 00:05:45.710 align:middle line:84%
and I began to become the
spiritual psychologist

00:05:45.710 --> 00:05:46.520 align:middle line:90%
that I now am.

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:49.410 align:middle line:90%


00:05:49.410 --> 00:05:52.650 align:middle line:84%
And shortly after that, I began
hearing these passages come

00:05:52.650 --> 00:05:56.310 align:middle line:84%
through my mind about
levels of consciousness

00:05:56.310 --> 00:05:58.290 align:middle line:84%
that I didn't
really know existed.

00:05:58.290 --> 00:06:00.180 align:middle line:90%
And I started taking notes.

00:06:00.180 --> 00:06:03.300 align:middle line:84%
And the book that I wrote,
which took four years to do,

00:06:03.300 --> 00:06:06.900 align:middle line:84%
is called "Transformers, The
Artists of Self-Creation."

00:06:06.900 --> 00:06:08.910 align:middle line:84%
And the book came about
just exactly the way

00:06:08.910 --> 00:06:11.264 align:middle line:84%
the message told
me that it would.

00:06:11.264 --> 00:06:12.930 align:middle line:84%
The message even went
further to tell me

00:06:12.930 --> 00:06:16.920 align:middle line:84%
that I would be guided
into meeting people who

00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:23.010 align:middle line:84%
would help me bring
forward my life's work.

00:06:23.010 --> 00:06:26.220 align:middle line:84%
And I do run a company now
called Eupsychia, which

00:06:26.220 --> 00:06:28.950 align:middle line:90%
means well-being in Greek.

00:06:28.950 --> 00:06:32.460 align:middle line:84%
And we're teaching people all
about soul-based psychology.

00:06:32.460 --> 00:06:34.440 align:middle line:84%
And it's all based
in the material

00:06:34.440 --> 00:06:37.245 align:middle line:84%
that came from that book that
day and came from that message.

00:06:37.245 --> 00:06:41.350 align:middle line:90%


00:06:41.350 --> 00:06:45.940 align:middle line:90%
And I'm just so grateful.

00:06:45.940 --> 00:06:48.130 align:middle line:84%
Because the book was
written exactly the way

00:06:48.130 --> 00:06:50.500 align:middle line:84%
the message told me
that it would be,

00:06:50.500 --> 00:06:55.240 align:middle line:84%
I really know now how it is
that our creativity happens.

00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:58.630 align:middle line:84%
It happens when our ego
gets out of the way,

00:06:58.630 --> 00:07:00.490 align:middle line:84%
and we're just wide
open, and we're

00:07:00.490 --> 00:07:03.520 align:middle line:84%
receiving a message
straight from our own higher

00:07:03.520 --> 00:07:04.810 align:middle line:90%
self, which is our soul.

00:07:04.810 --> 00:07:10.980 align:middle line:90%


00:07:10.980 --> 00:07:11.950 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm from New Jersey.

00:07:11.950 --> 00:07:13.408 align:middle line:10%
And I want to tell
you a story that

00:07:13.408 --> 00:07:16.150 align:middle line:10%
really transformed my life.

00:07:16.150 --> 00:07:19.390 align:middle line:10%
And I hope somehow this
will help someone out there.

00:07:19.390 --> 00:07:23.530 align:middle line:10%
About two years ago, I
went on a spiritual journey

00:07:23.530 --> 00:07:28.030 align:middle line:10%
with one of my friends and
we went out to New Mexico.

00:07:28.030 --> 00:07:32.290 align:middle line:10%
And we were going into the
mountains and praying every day

00:07:32.290 --> 00:07:35.050 align:middle line:10%
and asking Creator what we
can do to help heal the Earth

00:07:35.050 --> 00:07:38.260 align:middle line:10%
and make it a better
world and any way

00:07:38.260 --> 00:07:40.360 align:middle line:10%
that we could be of service.

00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:42.160 align:middle line:10%
And that was a
wonderful experience.

00:07:42.160 --> 00:07:46.720 align:middle line:84%
But the part that really
totally transformed my life

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:49.480 align:middle line:84%
was one evening,
during twilight time,

00:07:49.480 --> 00:07:51.280 align:middle line:84%
we went back to our
hotel room, which

00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:55.660 align:middle line:84%
was just this regular,
like, Motel 6 kind

00:07:55.660 --> 00:07:58.450 align:middle line:90%
of crummy, little hotel room.

00:07:58.450 --> 00:08:00.610 align:middle line:90%
And we're just sitting down.

00:08:00.610 --> 00:08:02.200 align:middle line:90%
She's on the bed.

00:08:02.200 --> 00:08:07.390 align:middle line:84%
And I'm sitting against the wall
with my back against the wall.

00:08:07.390 --> 00:08:11.200 align:middle line:84%
And it was, like, I said
twilight time outside.

00:08:11.200 --> 00:08:13.770 align:middle line:84%
And our room-- we had
purposely made it dark.

00:08:13.770 --> 00:08:18.520 align:middle line:84%
And we just put a candle out
so we could see each other.

00:08:18.520 --> 00:08:21.851 align:middle line:84%
And I'm looking at my
friend, and all of a sudden,

00:08:21.851 --> 00:08:24.100 align:middle line:84%
I felt like there was something
going on with my eyes.

00:08:24.100 --> 00:08:26.680 align:middle line:84%
But I said, Sandra, you're
not going to believe this.

00:08:26.680 --> 00:08:27.820 align:middle line:90%
She said, what is it?

00:08:27.820 --> 00:08:30.400 align:middle line:84%
I said you are
turning into light.

00:08:30.400 --> 00:08:32.429 align:middle line:84%
I said, I don't see
your body anymore.

00:08:32.429 --> 00:08:36.039 align:middle line:84%
All I see is your
outline with total light.

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:38.350 align:middle line:84%
And she said, Miriam, you're
not going to believe this.

00:08:38.350 --> 00:08:39.559 align:middle line:90%
I said, what is it?

00:08:39.559 --> 00:08:41.350 align:middle line:90%
And she said look at yourself.

00:08:41.350 --> 00:08:44.110 align:middle line:84%
So I looked at myself
and I was complete light.

00:08:44.110 --> 00:08:45.730 align:middle line:90%
And we weren't in meditation.

00:08:45.730 --> 00:08:48.440 align:middle line:84%
We weren't doing
anything special.

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:51.220 align:middle line:90%
It was just unbelievable.

00:08:51.220 --> 00:08:52.480 align:middle line:90%
We were both laughing.

00:08:52.480 --> 00:08:55.420 align:middle line:84%
I wasn't freaked out and
neither was she at the time.

00:08:55.420 --> 00:08:58.210 align:middle line:84%
I really felt like I had no
boundaries, that everything

00:08:58.210 --> 00:09:02.020 align:middle line:84%
was interconnected, that cosmic
consciousness of everything

00:09:02.020 --> 00:09:03.880 align:middle line:84%
being related and
interconnected,

00:09:03.880 --> 00:09:05.500 align:middle line:90%
and we're all one.

00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:08.350 align:middle line:90%
And sometimes we forget that.

00:09:08.350 --> 00:09:11.890 align:middle line:84%
So that revelation came
to me immediately, and so

00:09:11.890 --> 00:09:16.280 align:middle line:84%
did it come to my friend,
and it was just amazing.

00:09:16.280 --> 00:09:19.510 align:middle line:84%
So I went back to
where I was sitting.

00:09:19.510 --> 00:09:24.670 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden, I was
thinking home, going home.

00:09:24.670 --> 00:09:27.670 align:middle line:84%
And I felt all this love
and tremendous light

00:09:27.670 --> 00:09:31.030 align:middle line:84%
was coming into the
room, like waves

00:09:31.030 --> 00:09:34.280 align:middle line:84%
and waves of tremendous cosmic
love was coming into the room.

00:09:34.280 --> 00:09:36.070 align:middle line:90%
And we both felt it.

00:09:36.070 --> 00:09:38.890 align:middle line:84%
Then all of a sudden,
my friend says, Miriam,

00:09:38.890 --> 00:09:40.600 align:middle line:90%
you're starting to disappear.

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:42.130 align:middle line:90%
I said what?

00:09:42.130 --> 00:09:43.210 align:middle line:90%
So I looked at myself.

00:09:43.210 --> 00:09:46.370 align:middle line:84%
And actually, my legs
were no longer there.

00:09:46.370 --> 00:09:50.890 align:middle line:84%
And as I was looking up, there
was very little of me left.

00:09:50.890 --> 00:09:54.070 align:middle line:84%
And I realized I was going
up to that next level, which

00:09:54.070 --> 00:09:58.330 align:middle line:84%
is whatever you want to
call heaven or upper world.

00:09:58.330 --> 00:10:00.650 align:middle line:84%
And I knew if I had
gone the whole way,

00:10:00.650 --> 00:10:02.170 align:middle line:84%
I would not be
able to come back.

00:10:02.170 --> 00:10:05.230 align:middle line:84%
Something just said,
you know, in my head.

00:10:05.230 --> 00:10:08.015 align:middle line:84%
I knew that I would be
home and that would be it.

00:10:08.015 --> 00:10:09.640 align:middle line:84%
And she said to me,
you know you're not

00:10:09.640 --> 00:10:10.930 align:middle line:90%
supposed to go there yet.

00:10:10.930 --> 00:10:12.100 align:middle line:90%
You have to come back.

00:10:12.100 --> 00:10:14.710 align:middle line:84%
I said, I know, but I
don't want to come back.

00:10:14.710 --> 00:10:17.500 align:middle line:84%
I don't want to come
back, because there

00:10:17.500 --> 00:10:19.570 align:middle line:84%
was so much incredible
love, like I've never

00:10:19.570 --> 00:10:21.010 align:middle line:90%
felt in my life.

00:10:21.010 --> 00:10:25.000 align:middle line:84%
But I knew 1% in me
knew I had to come back

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:29.170 align:middle line:84%
because I have a purpose
here, just as we all do.

00:10:29.170 --> 00:10:32.230 align:middle line:84%
Right after it happened,
it was completely amazing

00:10:32.230 --> 00:10:33.490 align:middle line:90%
for both of us.

00:10:33.490 --> 00:10:37.510 align:middle line:84%
