00:14:50.620 --> 00:14:51.955 align:middle line:90%
I had to do drugs to function.

00:14:51.955 --> 00:14:55.689 align:middle line:90%


00:14:55.689 --> 00:14:57.480 align:middle line:84%
It's the only way that
I could do anything.

00:14:57.480 --> 00:14:59.880 align:middle line:84%
If I was going to work,
I had to do drugs.

00:14:59.880 --> 00:15:03.260 align:middle line:84%
If I was going to a
concert, I had to do drugs.

00:15:03.260 --> 00:15:05.540 align:middle line:84%
I had to do drugs sometimes
