00:16:20.215 --> 00:16:21.090 align:middle line:90%
It's a feeling that--

00:16:21.090 --> 00:16:23.430 align:middle line:84%
I mean, even to today, I
mean, I have told this story

00:16:23.430 --> 00:16:24.690 align:middle line:90%
