00:16:28.710 --> 00:16:31.410 align:middle line:90%
It was just a feeling that--

00:16:31.410 --> 00:16:35.510 align:middle line:84%
feeling worthless,
no respect from her.

00:16:35.510 --> 00:16:38.270 align:middle line:90%


00:16:38.270 --> 00:16:39.860 align:middle line:90%
It was just so devastating.

