00:21:05.310 --> 00:21:06.960 align:middle line:90%
And the woman walked in.

00:21:06.960 --> 00:21:09.600 align:middle line:84%
And he said, well,
this is Shuli Eshel.

00:21:09.600 --> 00:21:10.570 align:middle line:90%
I want you to meet her.

00:21:10.570 --> 00:21:11.940 align:middle line:90%
She wants to make a film.

00:21:11.940 --> 00:21:14.460 align:middle line:84%
This woman who walked
in, Miriam Spielman,

00:21:14.460 --> 00:21:18.840 align:middle line:84%
was one of the owners of
that big studio in Israel.

00:21:18.840 --> 00:21:21.570 align:middle line:84%
And she got very excited
about the subject.

00:21:21.570 --> 00:21:23.580 align:middle line:84%
And she then said,
well, how were

00:21:23.580 --> 00:21:24.930 align:middle line:90%
you thinking of paying for it?

00:21:24.930 --> 00:21:30.000 align:middle line:84%
And I took a pen and I wrote
down two shooting days, $3,000.

00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:32.310 align:middle line:84%
And at that moment,
I had a feeling

00:21:32.310 --> 00:21:35.520 align:middle line:84%
that I had to put my
mouth where my money was.

00:21:35.520 --> 00:21:38.490 align:middle line:84%
And I said, well,
I will pay 50%.

00:21:38.490 --> 00:21:40.020 align:middle line:90%
She took out her hand.

00:21:40.020 --> 00:21:41.460 align:middle line:90%
We shook hands.

00:21:41.460 --> 00:21:43.560 align:middle line:84%
And that was the beginning
of that documentary

00:21:43.560 --> 00:21:45.030 align:middle line:90%
that I produced.

00:21:45.030 --> 00:21:47.130 align:middle line:84%
At that time when I went
to Israel, I stayed.

00:21:47.130 --> 00:21:48.520 align:middle line:90%
I prolonged my stay.

00:21:48.520 --> 00:21:50.400 align:middle line:84%
And in five weeks,
I finished a film.

00:21:50.400 --> 00:21:53.080 align:middle line:90%


00:21:53.080 --> 00:21:56.320 align:middle line:84%
That night, I heard an
inner voice talk to me

00:21:56.320 --> 00:21:59.170 align:middle line:84%
and the inner voice
said that, as long

00:21:59.170 --> 00:22:04.150 align:middle line:84%
as I will be a good person
and bring love to the world

00:22:04.150 --> 00:22:07.660 align:middle line:84%
and live in balance and
not be greedy and be

00:22:07.660 --> 00:22:11.460 align:middle line:84%
participatory in life, I
will have everything I need

00:22:11.460 --> 00:22:13.570 align:middle line:90%
from that moment until I die.

00:22:13.570 --> 00:22:15.280 align:middle line:90%
>> The most important thing--

00:22:15.280 --> 00:22:17.440 align:middle line:90%
>> And that really happened.

00:22:17.440 --> 00:22:18.760 align:middle line:90%
I finished the film.

00:22:18.760 --> 00:22:20.740 align:middle line:84%
I went back to
the United States.

00:22:20.740 --> 00:22:23.890 align:middle line:90%
And money just started pouring.

00:22:23.890 --> 00:22:25.720 align:middle line:90%
My company flourished.

00:22:25.720 --> 00:22:29.110 align:middle line:84%
I had just started a company
a year and a half before that.

00:22:29.110 --> 00:22:31.420 align:middle line:84%
We were almost going
to close the company.

00:22:31.420 --> 00:22:33.260 align:middle line:90%
We had no money.

00:22:33.260 --> 00:22:35.170 align:middle line:90%
No projects were coming in.

00:22:35.170 --> 00:22:41.290 align:middle line:84%
And after that experience, which
I call a spiritual experience,

00:22:41.290 --> 00:22:45.280 align:middle line:84%
money just started pouring
and work started pouring in.

00:22:45.280 --> 00:22:49.690 align:middle line:84%
And it's just an amazing,
amazing turnaround

00:22:49.690 --> 00:22:51.160 align:middle line:90%
of events in my life.

00:22:51.160 --> 00:22:57.190 align:middle line:84%
And it's really, in some way, I
believe it is to do with trust

00:22:57.190 --> 00:23:01.690 align:middle line:84%
and believing in God and
trusting the universe.

00:23:01.690 --> 00:23:06.220 align:middle line:84%
And I just thought that
that would maybe, hopefully,

00:23:06.220 --> 00:23:10.560 align:middle line:84%
help and encourage and
inspire some other people.

00:23:10.560 --> 00:23:33.334 align:middle line:90%